OL,3,CJourney to tackle gender-based
OL,4,Cviolence must start in schools ` Yousaf
OL,6,FScotland's First Minister has said he
OL,7,Fhopes a new framework to help schools
OL,8,Ftackle gender-based violence will
OL,9,Fempower young people to be the
OL,10,F"generation that eradicates misogyny".
OL,12,FThe new Scottish Government framework
OL,13,Fhas been developed in collaboration
OL,14,Fwith Rape Crisis Scotland and Zero
OL,15,FTolerance, and features testimony from
OL,16,Fyoung people and school staff.
OL,18,FFirst Minister Humza Yousaf said that
OL,19,Fchange must happen at all levels of
OL,20,Fsociety and that "crucially that
OL,21,Fjourney must begin in our schools".
