OL,3,CJourney to tackle gender-based
OL,4,Cviolence must start in schools ` Yousaf
OL,6,FHe and Scotland's Education Secretary
OL,7,FJenny Gilruth will launch the new
OL,8,Fframework on Monday.
OL,10,FIt has been designed to support
OL,11,Fschools to tackle gender-based
OL,12,Fviolence, which refers to behaviours
OL,13,Franging from name calling,
OL,14,Fintimidation and physical violence to
OL,15,Fsexual harassment and emotional abuse.
