OL,3,CJourney to tackle gender-based
OL,4,Cviolence must start in schools ` Yousaf
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the launch, Mr
OL,7,FYousaf said: "Our Behaviour in
OL,8,FScottish Schools Research, published
OL,9,Fin November 2023, identified a rise in
OL,10,Fmisogyny as a worrying emerging trend
OL,11,Fwithin our schools.
OL,13,F"School staff pointed to an increase
OL,14,Fin sexist and misogynistic behaviour
OL,15,Famong male pupils, particularly
OL,16,Frelated to negative male role models
OL,17,Fonline.
