OL,3,CJourney to tackle gender-based
OL,4,Cviolence must start in schools ` Yousaf
OL,6,F"This was directed not only towards
OL,7,Ftheir peers, but also towards their
OL,8,Ffemale teachers, who of course make up
OL,9,Fthe majority of the teaching
OL,10,Fprofession.
OL,12,F"We must do everything we can to curb
OL,13,Fthe rise in such attitudes. It's time
OL,14,Fto raise the level of the conversation
OL,15,Fin our society, being frank about the
OL,16,Fimpact of the normalisation of
OL,17,Fmisogynistic behaviours and attitudes
OL,18,Fin our society that too often go
OL,19,Funchallenged.
