OL,3,CJourney to tackle gender-based
OL,4,Cviolence must start in schools ` Yousaf
OL,6,F"We will help to do that by providing
OL,7,Ftools to support a vision for a more
OL,8,Fpositive view of what masculinity
OL,9,Fmeans and why it is important.
OL,11,F"That must happen at all levels of
OL,12,Fsociety, and ` crucially ` that
OL,13,Fjourney must begin in our schools.
OL,15,F"By starting conversations amongst
OL,16,Fpupils that challenge societal views
OL,17,Fwhich normalise gender-based violence,
OL,18,Fit is my sincere hope that we can
OL,19,Fempower young people to be the
OL,20,Fgeneration that eradicates misogyny."
