OL,3,CJourney to tackle gender-based
OL,4,Cviolence must start in schools ` Yousaf
OL,6,FThe framework forms part of the
OL,7,FScottish Government's wider response
OL,8,Fto challenges with behaviour in
OL,9,Fschools.
OL,11,FMike Corbett, national official for
OL,12,Fthe NASUWT union, said: "Our research
OL,13,Finto behaviour in schools, coupled
OL,14,Fwith our casework, demonstrates that
OL,15,Fsexual harassment and sexist abuse
OL,16,Ftowards both female teachers and
OL,17,Fpupils in schools and colleges is
OL,18,Fcommonplace and that the majority of
OL,19,Fincidents fail to be reported or dealt
OL,20,Fwith effectively.
OL,26,@tD@YOU
