OL,3,CJourney to tackle gender-based
OL,4,Cviolence must start in schools ` Yousaf
OL,6,F"We welcome the commitment to tackling
OL,7,Fthe many forms of misogyny and
OL,8,Fsupporting effective practice in
OL,9,Fschools.
OL,11,F"This must also include equipping
OL,12,Fschools to confront sexism and
OL,13,Fmisogyny in the curriculum.
OL,15,F"Women and girls have a right to be
OL,16,Fafforded safety, security and respect
OL,17,Fat all times.
